---
title: Easy Peri-Peri Chicken & Haloumi Burger with Cheesy Potato Fries
description: Go international and dive into our new Burger collection; a selection of burger recipes inspired by different cuisines from across the world! Tonight, let us transport you to the shores of Portugal, home to the great Peri-Peri seasoning. Slathered onto juicy chicken breast and with a side of cheesy sweet potato fries, burger night has been sorted!
